title: "Dash Dolls" Star and Kardashian Bestie Malika Haqq Arrested for DUI Following Freeway Car Crash
text:
​After crashing her car early this morning on a freeway in Los Angeles, Malika Haqq — star of current E! series Dash Dolls — was arrested on a DUI charge. TMZ reports , citing police sources, that Malika failed a sobriety test administered at the scene of her crash, and showed "objective symptoms of intoxication." She told officers she had attended a party earlier in the evening.
Us Weekly adds that she was released Thursday afternoon, with her bail set at $30,000. While E!'s Dash Dolls is not believed to be filming currently, it remains to be seen if this incident will play out (or be recreated for, as Malika's BFF Khloé Kardashian's DUI was during Keeping Up With the Kardashians ' first season) on future episodes of the show.
